<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>wǒ men yào zàn měi yé hé huá 迦南1354</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 wǒ men yào zàn měi yé hé huá yīn wèi wàn yǒu dōu běn yú tā
 tā shì tiān de wàn yǒu de zhǔ zǎi zài wú bié shén néng xiàng tā
 wǒ men yào chēng xiè yé hé huá yīn tā de ài shǐ wǒ men qīn rú yī jiā
 bǐ cǐ dài dǎo bǐ cǐ xiāng ài xīn lǐ jiù lè kāi le huā
 zàn měi zhǔ ó chūn yǔ jiù jiàng xià gē shēng chuán biàn tiān yá
 chēng sòng zhǔ ó gē shēng bù tíng xià wàn guó wàn mín dōu yào jìng bài tā
 wàn guó wàn mín dōu yào jìng bài tā</lyrics>
<hymn_number>1354</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>